Requirements Elicitation:

Functional requirements:

FR1. SW must map chosen full-avatar elements
FR2. SW must link chosen full-avatar elements to minified equivalent
FR3. SW must reassemble mini-avater according to full-avatar
FR4. SW must provide a GUI to assemble full-avatar mapping
FR5. SW must PREVENT user from mapping incorrect element in a non compatible slot
     (ie: should not be able to place a hat on the feet)

Non-Functional requirements: NONE